summary: I STRAPPED MY SON INTO HIS GRACO CAR SEAT, WHICH I HAVE NEVER HAD A PROBLEM WITH BEFORE. IT WAS JUST A SMALL TRIP AND ON THE WAY THERE HIS SEAT WORKED PROPERLY.
